727224f-a.title: Queens: Liberty Avenue - 105th Street
727224f-a.text:
Liberty Avenue, at the N.E. corner of 105th Street. The
house was on the Andre Van Sicklen property in 1909. The view is
froa underneath the B.M.T. 'El.''
P. L. Sperr  March 10, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS

727225f-a.title: Queens: Liberty Avenue - 105th Street
727225f-a.text:
Liberty Ave., north side, between 105th and 106th Street,
showing the A. Van Sicklen house, erected about 1886 or 1887.
Eugene L. Armbruster states this house has been moved from the
above location. However, he does not state to what location.
August 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
